The urge to love someone little to much 
To become a little selfless for myself 
From being so mature to being so childish 
My every tantrum are now handle with care 
With all the love this world has offer me 
The space now which is given to me 
I can be who I want to be 
Truly transparent
I don't know if this is the end 
Or the beginning 
I hope this story never ends 
I hope it never stops 
I hope my story is complete with an happy ending 
After all it takes the story of an fantasy book 
Being lived by me in real world.
